      <title>BP 巴西总裁将在首席执行官离职后接管生物能源部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/bp-s-brazil-head-will-take-over-bioenergy-unit-after-ceo-exit</link>
